-- Chinatrust Interested in Nan Shan If Approached by AIG, President Wu Says
-- Yu-huay Sun
-- 2010-07-22T05:40:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-22/chinatrust-interested-in-nan-shan-if-approached-by-aig-president-wu-says.html

          
          
             Chinatrust Financial Holding Co.
would be interested in acquiring Nan Shan Life Insurance Co. if
approched by American International Group Inc., President Daniel
Wu said in Taipei today.  
